headline: Carrier Named to Inaugural Forbes Most Trusted Companies in America List
summary: Carrier Global Corporation (NYSE: CARR), global leader in intelligent climate and energy solutions, was recently named to Forbes' inaugural Most Trusted Companies in America 2025 list. This recognition highlights Carrier's commitment to fostering trust among its stakeholders and reflects the company's dedication to integrity and excellence.
